{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"cdb9a1947c","title":"林彪在《解放军报》元旦社论中的重要指示","origin":"《解放军报》1967年1月1日","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"7dc61e361e","index":0,"year":1967,"month":1,"day":1,"articleId":"cdb9a1947c"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"44b4a39710","name":"林彪","type":"人物"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"f326d8be5e","name":"林彪"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"6701fa4ffa","type":"title","text":"在《解放军报》元旦社论中的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"cdb9a1947c"},{"id":"8e9e398e8a","type":"authors","text":"林彪","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"cdb9a1947c"},{"id":"0f3420ccf9","type":"paragraph","text":"林彪同志根据毛主席历来的指示，根据毛主席提出的无产阶级革命事业接班人的五个条件，结合我军实际情况，提出了培养和选拔干部的三条标准。这就是：","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"cdb9a1947c"},{"id":"edb73db82a","type":"paragraph","text":"第一，高举毛泽东思想伟大红旗，忠于毛主席，忠于毛泽东思想；","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"cdb9a1947c"},{"id":"e196ff89e9","type":"paragraph","text":"第二，突出无产阶级政治，密切联系群众；","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"cdb9a1947c"},{"id":"33394f653c","type":"paragraph","text":"第三，有革命干劲。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"cdb9a1947c"},{"id":"83c6cc7a1e","type":"paragraph","text":" 《解放军报》1967年1月1日","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"cdb9a1947c"}],"page":{"id":"29d7b42207","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"cdb9a1947c","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}